description: Approval of reserved matters of layout, scale, appearance , access and landscaping, pursuant to Conditions B1, B8, Q1 and Q4 of the Stratford City Outline Planning Permission ( ref:10/90641/EXTODA) comprising the construction of buildings up to a maximum height of 16 storeys to provide 188 residential units and 649 sqm of complementary retail (Use Classes A1 - A5), with associated parking for cars, motorcycles, cycles and mobility scooters, vehicular access from De Coubertin Street and provision of public and private open space and landscaping, together with alterations to existing streetscape including; - provision of a loading bay on Celebration Avenue; - installation of dropped kerb s for provision of a loading bay/drop-off on De Coubertin Street; and - alterations to the location of existing parking spaces on De Coubertin Street
